OL,3,CDrop in child poverty in Scotland
OL,4,Csince targets introduced ` report
OL,6,FScotland has seen a 12% drop in child
OL,7,Fpoverty since introducing reduction
OL,8,Ftargets into law in 2017, according to
OL,9,Fnew research.
OL,11,FThere has been a reduction of 21,000
OL,12,Fchildren living in relative poverty,
OL,13,Fwhile in the same period, England and
OL,14,FWales have seen a 15% rise, said the
OL,15,FBig Issue.
OL,17,FThe magazine said its study
OL,18,Fhighlighted why Westminster should
OL,19,Fimplement similar poverty reduction
OL,20,Ftargets.
