OL,3,CDrop in child poverty in Scotland
OL,4,Csince targets introduced ` report
OL,6,FIts analysis of UK child poverty
OL,7,Fstatistics found that the assent of
OL,8,Fthe Child Poverty (Scotland) Act 2017
OL,9,Fwas a "parting of the ways" for the
OL,10,Fdifferent home nations' trajectories
OL,11,Fon child poverty.
OL,13,FThe report said a cyclical target-
OL,14,Fsetting method would translate
OL,15,FLabour's stated ambition of "enduring
OL,16,Fpoverty reduction" into concrete,
OL,17,Fmeasurable steps.
