OL,6,FLord John Bird, Big Issue founder and
OL,7,Fcrossbench peer, said: "With child
OL,8,Fpoverty in England and Wales predicted
OL,9,Fto rise to new pernicious highs, we
OL,10,Fcannot accept rhetoric in place of
OL,11,Freal change ` we must demand
OL,12,Fsustained, legislative action.
OL,14,F"Parliamentarians possess the
OL,15,Fauthority to drive this
OL,16,Ftransformation. Let us not look back
OL,17,Fand regret another missed opportunity.
OL,18,FThe time has come to stop simply
OL,19,Fmanaging poverty and to begin ending
OL,20,Fit."
